-- Mutual & Federal Chief Executive Kennedy to Retire in First Quarter 2011
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-07-27T14:50:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/mutual-federal-chief-executive-kennedy-to-retire-in-first-quarter-2011.html

          
          
             Mutual & Federal Insurance Co. Ltd.
said Chief Executive Officer Keith Kennedy will retire during
the first quarter of next year.  
 Kennedy will help the board appoint a replacement to ensure
a smooth transition, Johannesburg-based Mutual & Federal said in
an e-mailed statement today. Mutual & Federal, South Africaâ€™s
second-largest property and casualty insurer, is owned by
London-based Old Mutual Plc.  
          
          


  


        